<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Toxic-Teflon-Chemical-C8-Found-in-Tap-Water-in-Several-States-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Toxic-Teflon-Chemical-C8-Found-in-Tap-Water-in-Several-States-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/Toxic-Teflon-Chemical-C8-Found-in-Tap-Water-in-Several-States-200x150.jpg 200w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
</a>
